        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Well I have been mixed on this debate for quite sometime.  I think this anti-regen spell would help bring us back into the spotlight on all encounters.  Sure, make it like shaman slow, and then Spell casting Subletly is brought to the forefront where it should be.</P><P>Overpowering?  Limit to mobs that have over 32k hps and its not that overpowering.  Make it a high mana cost, say 600 mana and once again, it isnt overpowered.  The results would be worth it and lets all be honest.  People complain about spells making things trivial?  </P><P>HELLO!!!!</P><P>What do you think Clerics do already?</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=134799" target="_blank">Warlock of Terris-Thule</a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
